author: Debra Kahn and Carla Marinucci
title: Bend it like the Bay Area: Doctors hopeful about curve 2 weeks into shelter-in-place
description: After 14 days, doctors at area hospitals are now reporting fewer cases than they expected to see at this point.
content:
A relatively empty Golden Gate Bridge is seen March 27, 2020. | AP Photo
